SubjectRegulations Amending the Food and Drug Regulations (Vodka)
PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (VODKA) in order to amend the compositional standard for vodka to facilitate inter-provincial trade, harmonize more closely with trading partners, enable product innovation and allow distilleries to be more competitive and grow.
